(61, 60, 128, 1505492979, 'Is Macron the next Trump', 'is-macron-the-next-trump', 1, 'main', NULL, '1', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '<p>Who is Frances new president and where did he come from? Why did the French people decide on such a person and what will he bring to France? In this article we compare him to President Donald Trump of the USA. Although the two make not look like it, they are very similar as head of states.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>[nbsp]</p>\n<p><img src=\"files/Content/Galleries/Articles/MacronTrump/Macron.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"942\" height=\"470\"></p>\n<p>[nbsp]</p>', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '1', '', ''),
