(89, 7, 'tl_article', 512, 1505660961, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:16:\"English Teaching\";}', '<p class=\"p1\">I love to teach languages. I have been teaching English for the last 4 years and have enjoyed every moment of it. My lessons are funny and entertaining. That\'s always been important to me, without it I would have no passion for my teaching and my clients would be bored and learn nothing. After years of private lessons and professional teaching, I decided to start teaching online; this way I could see the world and keep my students. My relatonship to my students is also very important, having regular lessons and staying in contact is essential to have a productive and warm relationship.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:9:\"col-md-12\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
