(119, 52, 'tl_article', 240, 1505325704, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:14:\"Learning Style\";}', '<p>I think differently and I am definitely not[nbsp]not politically correct. I say what I want and you should too! Our lessons are a place for free discussion and debate. We like to teach English by discovering what the language really has to offer us. We learn by taking a closer look at world events, music, crime, drugs, history, new technologies and travel.[nbsp]We encourage co-operation and the involvement of friends. Anything that makes learning more fun, makes it easier. You can do a course online with your friends/colleagues in the same room or using different computers. The more people, the more fun.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:24:\"col-md-4 col-md-offset-1\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
