(191, 5, 'tl_news', 26, 1505916575, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:32:\"Killing the parasite of Facebook\";}', '<p>As mentioned, I recently removed myself from Facebook and Whatsapp. These are probably two of the best things that I\'ve done in a long time. I\'ve always known the evil sides of these services. After years of observing how they affected my life and reading enough about Facebooks data mining and social experimentation, I decided it was time to stop feed this filthy parasite my precious personal data</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
