(495, 9, 'tl_news', 256, 1505896566, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:19:\"Arrival in Valencia\";}', '<p>Being the tourist with money that I was back then, I bought myself a train ticket to Valencia. Nowadays I would have taken a bus or car sharing (using BlaBlaCar) or maybe hitchhiked as trains are an unnecessary luxury when you\'re a traveller who wants to go on travelling forever.It was a cool journey however, we went through the Catalan countryside and then along the coast. The Valencian countryside is very flat with lots of deserts and mountains. Quite a cool place to shoot a film I think[nbsp][nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(388, 7, 'tl_article', 520, 1505661297, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:14:\"Online Lessons\";}', '<p class=\"p1\">I moved to online teaching about 1 year ago. At that time I had no website of my own and advertised myself through Ebay Kleinanzeige, a German listing website, like Ebay but for jobs and local items. I always wanted to have my own website that was fully my own, no Wordpress bullshit, all me. So I began to teach myself web design, creating very basic pages and then moving on to more complex things. The first version of SamLernen was released in December 2016 and it was raw coded 100% by me. It was very buggy, unresponsive and slow. After a long and painful road of learning how to code and build complex database driven websites, I presented SamLernen to the world.[nbsp]</p>\n<p class=\"p1\">It has many features which are essential for my lessons, the most important and basic being an appointment calendar and a secure place to upload and view content, a place that was our very own! Now we have all this, it\'s working and it makes life a hell of a lot easier. Enjoy using the websites, theres more to come :D[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:9:\"col-md-12\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
