(461, 100, 'tl_article', 384, 1505840420, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h3\";s:5:\"value\";s:24:\"The problems with Macron\";}', '<p>Macron has been elected the new president of France.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>Emmanuel Macron[nbsp]won the 2017 French elections against Marine Le Pen with 73% of the votes. Marine Le Pen was seen as a more radical, right-wing politician who wanted France to leave the European Union.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>But who is this man and is he similar to Donald Trump?[nbsp]</p>\n<p>He is similar to president Trump in many ways. Both men have a background in business and finance, both presented themselves as \"political outsiders\" and both were unique candidates in their own way. Le Pen would be the first female president of France and Macron, with a background in investment banking and politics, created his own political party called[nbsp]<em>En Marche</em>[nbsp]and will be the youngest French head of state since Napoleon.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>[nbsp]</p>', '', 0x24e1e54c7d9311e7b1baec9b4278947f, '', '', 'a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"100\";i:1;s:3:\"100\";i:2;s:3:\"box\";}', 'a:5:{s:6:\"bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"left\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"right\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"top\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"unit\";s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'right', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(462, 100, 'tl_article', 512, 1505840420, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:29:\"Does Macron think like Trump?\";}', '<p>Macron is a very rich man who made a lot of money with investment banking at Rotschild [&] Cie Banque. The Rotschild family and its companies are infamous for it\'s enormous wealth and global political power. Many claim they form the \"Hidden Hand\", an elite group of extremely wealthy people, families and companies who[nbsp]<em>really</em>[nbsp]rule the world.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>[nbsp]</p>\n<p>Being a successful businessman like Macron or Trump means they must think and act according to simple rules</p>\n<p>[nbsp]</p>\n<p>1) Be open for negotiation, keep in mind needs of all participants</p>\n<p>2) Try to turn enemies into friends, war is too expensive</p>\n<p>3) Never dwell on[nbsp]your mistakes, business first.</p>\n<p>[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, 'bwa-GtWp4h4', NULL, 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
