(464, 100, 'tl_article', 640, 1505840420, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h3\";s:5:\"value\";s:40:\"Macron\'s wife is 24 years older than him\";}', '<p>Many find it strange how Macron is married toBriget Trogneux, who is 24 years older than him. Their love began when Macron was a 16 year old schoolboy and Bridget was his drama teacher at the school. His parents made him change schools as they were worried about this strange love affair, it didn\'t work and they married in 2007. This strange love affair contributed again to Macron\'s outsider image, others claim it is a[nbsp]<strong>sham marriage[nbsp]</strong>or that Macron is actually gay.[nbsp]In a way, this strange love affair a little similar to Melania Trump. For one, they both have big[nbsp]<strong>age differences</strong>[nbsp]to their husbands who are both the youngest and oldest ever presidents of their countries[nbsp]<strong>respectively</strong>.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, 'bwa-GtWp4h4', NULL, 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
