(466, 100, 'tl_article', 768, 1505840420, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h3\";s:5:\"value\";s:30:\"The media wanted Macron to win\";}', '<p>Unlike Trump in Ameria however, Macron was the media favourite. Macron is pro business and the media is big business. It is a business with enormous social power and in this case, it managed to contribute to the new president\'s victory. The media can influence any election by[nbsp]<strong>p</strong><strong>ainting their favourite candidate in a good light[nbsp]</strong>and making others look worse. In the example below, we can clearly see Le Pen being compared with Donald Trump.[nbsp]The media has[nbsp]<strong>done nothing but</strong>[nbsp]make Trump look bad all accross the world. People generally have negative feelings towards Trump. Despite Macron being more similar to trump in less obvious ways, the media used Le Pen\'s more radical opinions and even her hair to compare her to Trump.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, 'bwa-GtWp4h4', NULL, 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
