(511, 11, 'tl_news', 256, 1505902397, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:8:\"Alicante\";}', '<p>Ok so Alicante is where everything got a bit crazy. I arrived by train from Valencia because yet again I was being a posh tourist and decided to stay in a hostel. I thought it would be a good idea to do something like a rotation; one week hostel in one place, next week AirBnb in next place.</p>\n<p>The hostel was a really nice and colorful youth hostel which had a real party atmosphere. It had a lot of graffiti on the walls from guests and had a terrace with some sick psychadelic artwork. It was still winter time so there were few tourists and the prices were low. Prices per night at the hostel fluctuate between 13 and 20 euros a night between Summer and Winter.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(502, 9, 'tl_news', 1024, 1505900957, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:7:\"My host\";}', '<p>I rented a room for a week in an apartment in Valencia. I booked it through AirBnB, [nbsp]a relatively new, but verrrrry successful online app for holiday rentals. My host was a nice dude from Chile, he was into all the same rap music as me, so we chilled and had a barbeque on his roof terrace...in February. His flate mate was also great, for some reason I can\'t forget his face. He was also from Chile,but didn\'t work, rather just relaxed, played guitar and spent time with his son. He was so warm and friendly.</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, 'ce_dlh_googlemaps_default', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '0', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(503, 9, 'tl_news', 1152, 1505901235, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:26:\"Exploring Valencia by bike\";}', '<p>The next day, I went to the beautiful center of Valencia to go and rent myself a bike. On the first day I didn\'t find a bike rental shop, so I just walked around and took photos. The center, just like Barcelona, is a treat for the eyes. It\'s filled with traditional architcture, ancient remains and historical artifacts. The day after that I got my bike and took to the outskirts of the city. I first headed to the beach, which was much further away than I thought, I ended up [nbsp]in poor rural countryside very quick, It was like going from 2017 to 1917. I love how how such a part of the city area is so well preserved.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>After cycling for an hour I got to the beach. First cycled through the massive harbour complex and then onto the sprawling empty beach. It was too cold to swim so it was like a ghost town on the promenade. I took so many photos on those days, it felt so powerful and fantastic to cycle around a new country. Getting out all that bottled energy.</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, 'ce_dlh_googlemaps_default', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '0', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
