(505, 9, 'tl_news', 1408, 1505901582, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:22:\"Finding places to work\";}', '<p>Instead of taking time to enjoy my travels, I kept on giving my Skype lessons as if going to a new country to explore was an everyday thing for me. Well, I had moved from Germany to England and then to Spain all in the span of just 6 months. In Barcelona, I found it pretty difficult to keep up with my Skype lessons. I didn\'t have my macbook back then, just my shitty old laptop and my Ipad, I went to cafes and tried, but often times the coffee machines or the street noises were too loud and I had to cancel the lesson, other times I was just way too stoned.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>In Valencia, I didn\'t have this problem so much as I was staying in a quiet AirBnb with good, stable WIFI and not using the crappy hostel WIFI that a bunch of wannabe travellers are clogging up with their Facebook posts about how great ( *shit ) their holiday really is.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>[nbsp]</p>\n<p>[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, 'ce_dlh_googlemaps_default', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '0', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(506, 9, 'tl_news', 1536, 1505901767, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:16:\"Next destination\";}', '<p>My next destination was the sunny city of Alicante, 3 or 4 hours to the South of Valencia. It was a city I had been to before with my parents on my earlier travels as a child. My ultimate goal is to get to most Southern tip of Spain (Gibraltar) and then travel Portugal and head up North. Let\'s see how long that will take</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, 'ce_dlh_googlemaps_default', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '0', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
