(513, 11, 'tl_news', 1024, 1505902539, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:25:\"New friends at the hostel\";}', '<p>Really nice hostel, great parties and tonnes of girls that want to spend time with me. Above is one, we walked up to the castle together. I think her name was Cleopatra. Nice girl. I\'ve been thinking of returning there to make some more contacts. I\'m always searching for other digital nomads who are into teaching, translating and web design/development and I met one of my best friends, Toby, at the hostel. He is also a web developer and travels around Spain on his money he earns from that. [nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, 'ce_dlh_googlemaps_default', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '0', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(514, 11, 'tl_news', 1152, 1505902677, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:14:\"Alicante beach\";}', '<p>[nbsp]</p>\n<p>After a night of partying at the hostel, drinking lots of alcohol and smoking lots of weed from the local cannabis assosciation, we would hit the beach. It was still winter, but midday temperatures could reach up to 18 degrees. The water was still way too cold to swim in though, although I remember one guy from England (also called Sam) went into the cold water and came out freezing. Funny I mention him, because at one time in my 2 weeks in this hostel there were 5 guys all from England called Sam[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, 'ce_dlh_googlemaps_default', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '0', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(522, 12, 'tl_news', 256, 1505915944, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:7:\"Almeria\";}', '<p>After spending two weeks in Orihuela costa, in the middle of crazy-nowhere town, I decided to come back to Alicante for a few days and then head off for Almeria. I had seen that apartments were very cheap in Almeria and had heard that food was also very tasty and cheap too. I decided this was the place for me, and so it was my home for about 3 months.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '');
