(526, 12, 'tl_news', 1408, 1505915928, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:14:\"Apartment life\";}', '<p>My new apartment was just amazing, I feel so lucky to have lived there for such a low price. Almeria is such a wonderful city, so unspoiled by tourism like so many other parts of Spain. It\'s so Spanish and so well preserved that you feel like you\'re living in the 1980\'s or 1990\'s. Almeria is the capital of the Almeria region, which grows so much fruit and vegetables that they export around 70% of it to the rest of Europe This all meant that food in Almeria was VERY cheap.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>Noy only had I found a beautiful, preserved and cheap city, I had found a 200 euro a month apartment on the beach with a weed dealer neighbour and beautiful girls recently visiting.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, 'ce_dlh_googlemaps_default', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '0', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(529, 5, 'tl_news', 28, 1505916659, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:24:\"Growing up with Facebook\";}', '<p>Facebook is something I can really say I\'ve grown up with, not like the children of this generation, but almost. I began using Facebook when it became popular in my school at around age 14. A very vulnerable age. I was completely hooked to the flurry of information and attention I was getting and could give. I could look at all my crushes, they could look at me, I could stalk people, I could remember peoples names and birthdays. How fantastic...it seemed[nbsp]</p>\n<p>I never stopped to think that Facebook was genuinely spying on me. I never read the terms and conditons. I didn\'t give a shit. Now Facebook knows almost everything about me such as</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Who my friends are</li>\n<li>Who my parents are</li>\n<li>Where I lived</li>\n<li>How I look[nbsp]</li>\n<li>My entire personality[nbsp]</li>\n</ul>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, 'ce_dlh_googlemaps_default', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '0', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(527, 12, 'tl_news', 1536, 1505915874, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:34:\"Begining work on the new SamLernen\";}', '<p>On coming to Almeria, I had the intention of setting aside some time to really crack the books and learn. I wanted to build SamLernen. I wanted it to be big and impressive, I wanted to learn everything there was to learn about web design and development so I could achieve this. In Almeria I spend countless days indoors getting high and learning all about web development/coding and more about computer science in general. Computer science has always been my second academic passion, alongside languages.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, 'ce_dlh_googlemaps_default', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '0', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(530, 5, 'tl_news', 30, 1505916818, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:17:\"Living without it\";}', '<p>Many people have trouble deleting Facebook, we always want to, but don\'t want to feel left out. If this is the case then you should take a closer look at your life. Why do you have friends that make you use an evil service? A service which sells your personal information to advertisers and is probably the biggest driver in the direction of transforming society into a Orwellian techno-police state, with the cameras everywhere recognising your face through Facebook, police predicting who will be a criminal based on their Facebook and god knows what else diabolical things artificial intelligence and Facebook can achieve together[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, 'ce_dlh_googlemaps_default', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '0', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
